name: ISO 8601 & Big Endian
description: Parses big endian and ISO 8601 formatted dates, such as the below: 1983-03-15T20:30:30.09000001983-W14-041983-0901983.03.31 8:30:30 PMGroups are as follows: 1=Year2=Day of Year3=Month4=Week of Year5=Day of Week6=Day of Month7=Hour of Day8=Minute of Hour9=Second of Minute10=Fractions of Second11=AM/PM flag12=Timezone13=GMT Offset Multipliet14=GMT Hour Offset15=GMT Minute Offset
author: jakbutler
